description: Edelweiss Mutual Fund - Edelweiss ETF - Nifty 100 Quality 30 is an exchange traded fund launched by Edelweiss Financial Services Limited. It is managed by Edelweiss Asset Management Limited. The fund invests in the public equity markets of India. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. It seeks to replicate the performance of the Nifty Quality 30 Index, by investing in the stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. The fund was formerly known as Edelweiss Mutual Fund - Edelweiss ETF - Nifty Quality 30. Edelweiss Mutual Fund - Edelweiss ETF - Nifty 100 Quality 30 was formed on May 12, 2016 and is domiciled in India.
name: Edelweiss ETF - Nifty 100 Quality 30
